responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D7AAC6DA4DF200E48EB68594B3C91A02", "He\'ll be wearing a medallion with an oakleaf motif, so bring it to the receivers as proof of your accomplishments. It\'s probably his prized possession, and the poor fellow probably never leaves home without it. Values it more than his very own life, I gather. The order says this happens before the carnival hits the main roads. You better get going sooner rather than later.")
